    - target: {fileID: 6549579016455550173, guid: 112c25ea93ff2de488deb0ea970001be, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'How good is your visual memory? Follow the rhythm of the lights and
        don''t make mistakes.


        Watch: The game will show a sequence of colors
        (Red, Yellow, Green, and Blue).


        Repeat: Press the buttons in the
        same order they appeared.


        The Challenge: Every time you win a turn,
        a new color is added to the pattern.


        Reward: The game ends if you
        make a mistake. The more turns you win, the more coins you get!'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
